    %h5 The Goal
    %p
      The primary goal of the Cambridge Inventors Club is to create a safe, healthy,
      interesting, and fun environment for young people to explore creative problem
      solving through the lens of technical skills such as coding and engineering.
    %p
      We bring together volunteers from the technology community in the general
      area around Kendall Sq and Cambridge to both support students in their work
      and to connect students with a variety of adults working in various technological
      fields.

