    %h5 The Results So Far
    %p
      We've now run the program for two eight-week sessions and we continue to evolve and improve
      the design. What started out primarily as a coding program has evolved to become more
      hands-on and creative with a focus on invention.
    %p
      Most importantly the students are increasingly taking ownership of the environment,
      reflecting on everything from the challenges to the rules to the overall environment
      and providing us with feedback. This allows us to continue evolving the program in
      a direction that better meets the needs and interests of the students.



